<li><p>(17.4) &mdash; <tt>is_default_constructible_v&lt;Allocator&gt;</tt> is `true`.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>
<ins>-?- <i>Mandates:</i> <tt>is_constructible_v&lt;T, U&gt;</tt> is `true`.</ins>
<p/>
-18- <i>Effects</i>: [&hellip;]
</p>
